{"tid":692395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★無家者增因難負擔租金　NGO憂更多劏房戶「瞓街」","createTime":"2018-06-06T15:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T16:00:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41f4c2efb092a075104644740772f6f30e13063a","tid":692395,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「棺材房」月租3年間升幅近5成</span><br />\n<br />\n救世軍社區計劃高級主任馬澤淳指出，在過去3年間面積僅得十多平方呎的「棺材房」，其月租由約1,300元攀升至1,900元，租金升幅約46%。<br />\n<br />\n根據社署過往5年數據顯示，已登記的露宿者人數在17/18年有1,127人，較去年的924人增逾200人，增幅近兩成。而他們露宿原因，大都是因為失業無力支付租金需要露宿街頭，亦有人因為找不到可負擔租金的居所只好露宿。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「有公屋住我連租都畀唔起」</span><br />\n<br />\n流落街頭逾十載的61歲陳伯，目前「居住」在位於新蒲崗的運動館外。採訪當晚氣溫高達攝氏34度，陳伯赤裸上身、滿頭大汗坐在石椅上，等待旁邊籃球場於晚上11時關燈後才入睡。<br />\n他笑說，作為無家者須學會適者生存，經歲月洗禮後，已習慣嘈吵的居住環境，惟遇到寒風刺骨的寒冷天氣，叫他無法忍受：「熱咪去沖涼，但凍到頂唔順，就真係要去避寒中心！」<br />\n陳伯曾領取綜援金生活及租住劏房，但過往長期間於內地工作，因此失去領取綜援資格；回港後僅拾荒維生，無法承擔劏房租金，令他被迫成為無家者：「屋企人陪我去申請排公屋，但有公屋住，我連租都畀唔起。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/194540/%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%85%E5%A2%9E%E5%9B%A0%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91-ngo%E6%86%82%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6-%E7%9E%93%E8%A1%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F194540%2F%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%259B%25A0%25E9%259B%25A3%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E6%2593%2594%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591-ngo%25E6%2586%2582%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6-%25E7%259E%2593%25E8%25A1%2597&d=kV2Lz1FzZgpehjoPeQXrLb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=cc8a14bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/194540/%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%85%E5%A2%9E%E5%9B%A0%E9%9B%A3%E8%B2%A0%E6%93%94%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91-ngo%E6%86%82%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%88%B6-%E7%9E%93%E8%A1%97</a>"},{"pid":"89edd8cb16d40ecd2d6fffaaa03aaacff1e43ee7","tid":692395,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1499729/org/b23f2169cd2f34e56496e1197f125861.jpg/0B682mCXy5sxVy5P7NjJv8rkf5TGmvAdhH8MCoR_DAo?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1499729%2Forg%2Fb23f2169cd2f34e56496e1197f125861.jpg%2F0B682mCXy5sxVy5P7NjJv8rkf5TGmvAdhH8MCoR_DAo%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=f8c826aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳伯露宿在新蒲崗的運動館外。（羅君豪攝）"},{"pid":"d8824eec5738b3b2c4db6f09537bf08e6cfd8097","tid":692395,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"more better<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/215223_b4ef4ae4853602df0fb9d0432c4b8840.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F215223_b4ef4ae4853602df0fb9d0432c4b8840.png&h=2d9713f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/ftp/News/20150819/HK/_19gm303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20150819%2FHK%2F_19gm303.jpg&h=0e6d59be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9171cf765578125581f04539b3f98ec6176893c","tid":692395,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"冇屋住要露宿,遲早再佔中集體露營"},{"pid":"9464e9bcc6460a8908fd44130c63e7e97e7d9305","tid":692395,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9171cf765578125581f04539b3f98ec6176893c","tid":692395,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:28